27:32.580 --> 27:34.010
Matron Qiao, lebih dekat.

27:34.040 --> 27:34.630
Baiklah.

27:35.990 --> 27:37.790
Tiga, dua, satu.

27:37.850 --> 27:38.880
Senyum.

27:38.990 --> 27:39.830
Senyum.

27:40.740 --> 27:41.350
Minumlah.

