28:08.340 --> 28:08.930
Betul.

28:09.390 --> 28:10.370
Taklah.

28:10.550 --> 28:12.070
Saya rasa rakan sama bidang agak baik.

28:12.470 --> 28:13.140
Lagipun,

28:13.350 --> 28:14.510
