28:33.350 --> 28:33.950
Mana mungkin?

28:33.950 --> 28:34.470
Taklah.

28:34.760 --> 28:36.290
Selagi mereka bersatu hati.

28:36.310 --> 28:36.970
Betul.

28:38.140 --> 28:39.350
Selagi hubungan mereka baik.

28:39.990 --> 28:40.510
Kamu...

28:41.070 --> 28:42.030
Ada orang nak minum minuman?

28:43.240 --> 28:44.200
Cola tanpa gula.

28:44.790 --> 28:45.920
