29:16.670 --> 29:17.030
Jom.

29:19.130 --> 29:19.750
Lu Yan.

29:22.120 --> 29:22.840
Abang senior.

29:24.010 --> 29:25.220
Semua orang tengah tunggu awak.

29:25.990 --> 29:26.670
Kita berjumpa lagi.

29:27.480 --> 29:28.830
Tak sangka awak datang juga.

29:29.590 --> 29:30.590
Dia ajak saya.

29:31.190 --> 29:31.770
Jom.

29:32.580 --> 29:32.990
Jom.

29:33.010 --> 29:34.060
Saya hampir mati kelaparan.

29:41.190 --> 29:42.160
Qianqian.

29:42.590 --> 29:43.100
Qianqian.

29:43.150 --> 29:43.590
Dah datang.

29:43.610 --> 29:44.590
Yan, awak datang.

29:44.710 --> 29:45.270
Jiang, kenapa awak datang?

29:45.270 --> 29:46.110
Ketua Jiang, awak juga datang.

29:46.310 --> 29:47.510
Hadiah yang saya dan Lu Yan beli untuk awak.

29:47.510 --> 29:48.270
Terima kasih.

29:49.150 --> 29:50.230
Kenapa Ketua Jiang

29:50.270 --> 29:51.110
