30:00.170 --> 30:00.630
Marilah.

30:01.150 --> 30:01.510
Baiklah.

30:01.530 --> 30:02.270
Awak duduk di sini.

30:03.100 --> 30:03.770
Lu Yan,

30:03.830 --> 30:05.650
