32:32.840 --> 32:33.440
Saya...

32:33.630 --> 32:34.470
Betul.

32:34.500 --> 32:35.600
Awak tak boleh minum lagi.

32:36.030 --> 32:37.110
Kami cuma rakan universiti.

32:37.130 --> 32:39.640
Apabila di universiti,

32:40.220 --> 32:41.790
